      "description": "The CFD model of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump produces hemolysis index predictions of sufficient fidelity to support identification of worst-case operating conditions across the five CPB flow-speed combinations. The model meets all seven assessed credibility factors at or above the required level for Model Risk Level 2, and the relative hemolysis index satisfies the RH < 1 acceptance criterion for a Class II device under cardiopulmonary bypass use.",
